          <div class="area-desc">User spent significant time invoking local slash commands to configure Claude Code settings, including model selection, themes, TUI, plan mode, effort levels, plugins, and integrations like Slack and Chrome. These sessions were primarily exploratory configuration rather than task-driven work.</div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="project-area">
          <div class="area-header">
            <span class="area-name">CLAUDE.md Documentation Generation</span>
            <span class="area-count">~1 sessions</span>
          </div>
          <div class="area-desc">User ran /init to generate and update project documentation. In one successful case, Claude identified three specific issues (missing prefix, stale script reference, missing invocation example) and applied edits; another attempt failed because the working directory was empty.</div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="project-area">
          <div class="area-header">
            <span class="area-name">Debug &amp; Session Troubleshooting</span>
